'''''Kaatrinile Varum Geetham''''' ({{lit|The song wafts into the air}}) is a [[1978 in film|1978]] [[Tamil language|Tamil]] [[Cinema of India|Indian]] [[feature film]], [[Film director|directed]] by [[S. P. Muthuraman]] for Vijayabhaskar Films. The film stars [[Muthuraman (actor)|Muthuraman]] and [[Kavitha (actress)|Kavitha]] in the lead roles.<ref>{{cite web|title=Kaatrinile Varum Geetham LP Vinyl Records|url=http://musicalaya.net/imgviewer.php?mod=lpcovers/369/3/1/1|publisher=musicalaya|accessdate=2014-05-02|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502072056/http://musicalaya.net/imgviewer.php?mod=lpcovers%2F369%2F3%2F1%2F1|archivedate=2 May 2014|df=dmy-all}}</ref>

== Cast ==

*[[Muthuraman (actor)|Muthuraman]] as Mohan
*[[Kavitha (actress)|Kavitha]] as Geetha/Kamini/Rosy
*[[Thengai Srinivasan]] as Chandran
*[[Sreekanth]] as James
*[[S. A. Ashokan]] as Veerayan - Kamini's father
*[[M. N. Rajam]] as Mohan's mother
*[[Major Sundarrajan]]
*[[Sukumari]]
*[[Y. G. Mahendra]] as flight passenger
*[[Usilaimani]] as flight passenger

